    • Field Detail

      • MFG_CAGE_CODE

        public static final java.lang.String MFG_CAGE_CODE
        The mfgCageCode attribute represents the reference to the manufacturing organization for the part instance. Used to indicate the Manufacturing ID for the company that manufactured the part instance. Conceptually on the part instance, it is actually implemented on the master. Needs to be called mfgCageCode(because it has migration implications for the Windchill A&D module).

        Supported API: true

        See Also:
